@BryanRansil The app TFLiteObjectDetectionAPIModel.java references a COCO dataset pre-trained Mobilenet V1 SSD by default. Did the app build with pre-trained model?
In the blog post, we provided instructions to finetune weights for Pets dataset and provided the corresponding TF Lite files.
On your last question, we can double check if V2 SSD is working.
